<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddd091819-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s2231"><num value="2231">§ 2231.</num><heading> Establishment and accounts</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is established in the Treasury of the United States a revolving fund to be known as the Capitol Visitor Center Revolving Fund (in this section referred to as the “Fund”), consisting of the following individual accounts:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="iddd09181a-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s2231/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The Gift Shop Account.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="iddd09181b-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s2231/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The Miscellaneous Receipts Account.</content>
</paragraph>
